description:
Bon Jovi is the debut album of American heavy metal band Bon Jovi, released on January 21, 1984. Produced by Tony Bongiovi and Lance Quinn, it is significant for being the only Bon Jovi album on which a song ("She Don't Know Me") appears that was not written nor co-written by members of the band. The album charted at #43 on The Billboard 200.

The album was ranked the 11th best rock album of 1984 by Kerrang! magazine.
